# Personal Assistant Memory Engine / PAME (Phase 31)

Read **[ASSISTANT_MEMORY_ENGINE.md](../../ASSISTANT_MEMORY_ENGINE.md)** before assistant chat, memory, or reminder changes.

## Rules

1. **Build an assistant, not a chatbot** — natural language in, intention understood, follow-up questions out
2. **Metadata only** — never store raw chat transcripts; summaries max 500 chars
3. **PAME supports the user** — distinct from **Learning Engine** (`customer_learning_memory`) which improves Aipify
4. Customer routes: `/app/assistant`, `/app/assistant/memory` — APIs at `/api/assistant/*`
5. Confidence model: high (explicit) stores; medium asks confirm; low never auto-stores
6. Always ask before remembering when uncertain (`ask_before_remembering` default true)
7. User ownership: view, edit, pause, complete, delete, export — admins cannot access memory content
8. Platform aggregates only at `/platform/trust` — `privacy_note` on overview RPC
9. i18n: `locales/{en,no,sv,da}/customerApp.json` (`assistant.*`, `assistantMemory.*`)
10. **Human Memory Intent Dataset v1.0** — read [HUMAN_MEMORY_INTENT_DATASET.md](../../HUMAN_MEMORY_INTENT_DATASET.md); extend `memory-intent-dataset.ts` for new natural phrasing, not command syntax

